<A>__{in the darkness we hear dripping water, the echoing approach of two sets of footsteps. there is the sound of a sudden, quick scuffle, a heavy fall of bodies. three booming gunshots. two from one gun, one from another. so fast and close, they're barely distinguish able. the sound of the shots echoes against concrete walls and dies away. silence. slow, slow, fade in:}
